   iniTime \<le> endTime \<Longrightarrow>
   reduceContractStep \<lparr>timeInterval = (iniTime, endTime)\<rparr> (sta\<lparr>minTime := iniTime\<rparr>) c = NotReduced \<Longrightarrow> c = Close"
  apply (cases c)
  apply blast
